<P>A SHORT Catechi&s;m Drawn out of the WORD OF GOD.</P>
<P>By <HI>Samuel Stone,</HI> Pastor of the Word at <HI>Hartford</HI> on CONNECTICOT.</P>
<P>Printed by <HI>Bartholomew Green, and John Allen,</HI> for <HI>William Gibbons.</HI> 1699.</P>
